data.description: Incredible West Knox location! Features a gorgeous open floor plan including living room  with vaulted ceilings and a gas fireplace. Youll love the open kitchen with pantry and granite counters. The home has a main level primary bedroom, large walk in closet, and bathroom. This home has an extra bedroom and full bathroom downstairs as well as a laundry room. Upstairs you will find an office, bonus room/loft area, 2 large bed rooms and a full bathroom. There are two linen closets upstairs with walk in storage to the attic. This home also has a two car attached garage, a deck, and a fenced back yard.
